data.description: Discover the potential of this charming fixer-upper nestled on a spacious, mature lot with a generously sized fenced-in backyard! Boasting four bedrooms and a large loft, this home provides ample space for your family's needs.The main floor features a master bedroom complemented by a formal dining room and a great room that seamlessly opens to the kitchen. Step onto the newly re-framed screened porch, an ideal spot to unwind and enjoy the outdoor ambiance.While this home requires a bit of tender loving care, it presents a fantastic opportunity to secure a larger home at an appealing price point. With a little elbow grease you can bring your vision to life! Embrace the endless possibilities for customization and  imagine the satisfaction of turning this diamond in the rough into aresidence that perfectly suits your lifestyle. This home can become the canvas for your dream home journey. Don't miss out on the chance to make it yours!    Located in the highly desired Dorchester 2 school district, this neighborhood is close to everything you need! You will be just minutes from shopping, Joint Base Charleston, I-526, Charleston airport, Park Circle and your choice of restaurants.  It's also just a short drive to downtown Charleston and the beaches!
